description.standard:
*** Featured as Best New Apps in more than 96 countries ***

*** Featured by Apple in Social Networking and Books Apps *** 

20lines is the best place to write, read and share stories!

We all have a story to tell. Share yours in 3 simple steps or browse among thousands of short stories on any topic or genre.

20lines lets you:
- Write a new story at anytime: you can save the draft or post it directly with an amazing cover
- Discover thousands of new stories, have a look at the popular ones, browse your favorite channels or see what are the trending hashtags
- Read and interact with the author: vote the story, leave a comment or share it on the social networks
- Create your profile and discover other 20liners. Follow the authors you prefer and chat with them

We’re always interested in hearing your comments and suggestions. Tweet us as @20lines or @20lineshelp for support or send us an email with your feedbacks to hello@20lines.com!
